Distribution: Central European Alps ( France , Switzerland , Italy , Austria , Romania ) and Arctic Fennoscandia (
ssp. quenseli
); eastern Siberia, west to the Amur region (
ssp. liturata
), and Hokkaido , Japan (
ssp. daisetsuzana
